--------------------------------------------------------------
Initial Things to do :

Initialise package.json:
npm init -y

Install Express and Nodemon :
npm install express
npm install -g nodemon  // nice server 

To run Server or Any File:
nodemon index.js

Add this in package.json to make the project as ES6:
"type": "module"    

